*lynx-2.8.9_pre6 (25 Aug 2015)

  25 Aug 2015; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> +lynx-2.8.9_pre6.ebuild:
  version bump

  26 Aug 2015; Mike Frysinger <vapier@gentoo.org> lynx-2.8.8_p2.ebuild,
  lynx-2.8.9_pre4.ebuild, lynx-2.8.9_pre6.ebuild:
  sys-libs/ncurses: move to SLOT=0 #557472

  Use SLOT=0 for installing of main development files like other packages
  so we can use other SLOTs for installing SONAME libs for binary packages.

